Definition: phenomenon exhibited by materials like copper or bismuth that become magnetized in a magnetic field with a polarity opposite to the magnetic force
Example: unlike iron they are slightly repelled by a magnet
Synonyms: adj, pert, diamagnetic, magnetism, phenomenon, exhibited, by, materials, like, copper, or, bismuth, that, become, magnetized, in, a, magnetic, field, with, polarity, opposite, to, the, force, unlike, iron, they, are, slightly, repelled, magnet
Category: noun.phenomenon
